item.title: Financial Deposits UI
item.description: Financial deposit UI system helps to automate the manual process of cheques received for various insurance policies and submission to the bank in electronic form. With the help of this system all the cheques received by the company processed electronically and ICL file is created which is sent to bank for cheques deposit process.
